!!!
%html{lang: "en"}
  %head
    %meta{charset: "UTF-8"}/
    %meta{content: "IE=edge,chrome=1", "http-equiv" => "X-UA-Compatible"}/
    %meta{content: "width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0", name: "viewport"}/
    %title Fullscreen Layout with Page Transitions
    %meta{content: "Fullscreen Layout with Page Transitions", name: "description"}/
    %meta{content: "fullscreen layout, boxes, responsive, page transitions, css transitions, jquery, portfolio, template", name: "keywords"}/
    %meta{content: "Codrops", name: "author"}/
    %link{href: "../favicon.ico", rel: "shortcut icon"}/
    %link{href: "css/component.css", rel: "stylesheet", type: "text/css"}/
    %script{src: "js/modernizr.custom.js"}
  %body
    .container
      #bl-main.bl-main
        %section
          .bl-box
            -# Donate ----------------------------------------------------------------
            %h2.bl-icon.bl-icon-gift.gray Donate
          .bl-content
            = row :page_message do
              %h2 Donation
            = row :instructions do
              .columns.small-12
                %p.instructions-step Step 1. Find a need in our community that you may be able to fill.
                = search_bar 'What would you like to donate?'
            .row
              .columns.small-12
                = button_tag :query, class: "btn" do
                  SEARCH NEEDS
          %span.bl-icon.bl-icon-close
        %section#bl-work-section
          .bl-box
            -# Sell --------------------------------------------------------------------
            %h2.bl-icon.bl-icon-sell.white Sell
          .bl-content
            = row :page_message do
              %h2.bright-white Sell
              %p.bright-white Sell unwanted goods, and donate up to 100% of the proceeds to the non-profit of your choice
            = row do
              .columns.small-12
                = link_to new_merchandise_path,
                  class: 'btn' do
                  Sell
          %span.bl-icon.bl-icon-close.bright-white
        %section
          .bl-box
            -# Shop --------------------------------------------------------------------
            %h2.bl-icon.bl-icon-shop.white Shop
          .bl-content
            %h2 Shop
            %p Browse our marketplace. Portions of each purchase are donated to local nonprofits.
            = row do
              .columns.small-12
                = link_to merchandises_path,
                  class: 'btn' do
                  Shop Now
          %span.bl-icon.bl-icon-close 
        %section
          .bl-box
            -# Join -------------------------------------------------------------------
            %h2.bl-icon.bl-icon-join.gray Join
          .bl-content
            %h2 Join
            = row :page_message do
              .columns.small-12
                %h3 Join our community!
            = row :user_type do
              .columns.small-6.text-center
                %h3.padded Are you an organization?
                =link_to new_organization_registration_path, class: "btn dark" do
                  Organization Sign Up
              .columns.small-6.text-center
                %h3.padded Are you an individual?
                =link_to new_individual_registration_path, class: "btn dark" do
                  Individual Sign Up
          %span.bl-icon.bl-icon-close 
        -#/ Panel items for the works
        #bl-panel-work-items.bl-panel-items
          %div{"data-panel" => "panel-1"}
            %div
              %img{src: "images/1.jpg"}/
              %h3 Fixie bespoke
              %p Iphone artisan direct trade ethical Austin. Fixie bespoke banh mi ugh, deep v vinyl hashtag. Tumblr gentrify keffiyeh pop-up iphone twee biodiesel. Occupy american apparel freegan cliche. Mustache trust fund 8-bit jean shorts mumblecore thundercats. Pour-over small batch forage cray, banjo post-ironic flannel keffiyeh cred ethnic semiotics next level tousled fashion axe. Sustainable cardigan keytar fap bushwick bespoke.
          %div{"data-panel" => "panel-2"}
            %div
              %img{src: "images/2.jpg"}/
              %h3 Chillwave mustache
              %p Squid vinyl scenester literally pug, hashtag tofu try-hard typewriter polaroid craft beer mlkshk cardigan photo booth PBR. Chillwave 90's gentrify american apparel carles disrupt. Pinterest semiotics single-origin coffee craft beer thundercats irony, tumblr bushwick intelligentsia pickled. Narwhal mustache godard master cleanse street art, occupy ugh selfies put a bird on it cray salvia four loko gluten-free shoreditch.
          %div{"data-panel" => "panel-3"}
            %div
              %img{src: "images/3.jpg"}/
              %h3 Austin hella
              %p Ethical cray wayfarers leggings vice, seitan banksy small batch ethnic master cleanse. Pug chillwave etsy, scenester meh occupy blue bottle tousled blog tonx pinterest selvage mixtape swag cosby sweater. Synth tousled direct trade, hella Austin craft beer ugh chambray.
          %div{"data-panel" => "panel-4"}
            %div
              %img{src: "images/4.jpg"}/
              %h3 Brooklyn dreamcatcher
              %p Fashion axe 90's pug fap. Blog wayfarers brooklyn dreamcatcher, bicycle rights retro YOLO. Wes anderson lomo 90's food truck 3 wolf moon, twee jean shorts. Iphone small batch twee wolf yr before they sold out. Brooklyn echo park cred, portland pug selvage flannel seitan tousled mcsweeney's.
          %nav
            %span.bl-next-work > Next Project
            %span.bl-icon.bl-icon-close
    / /container
    %script{src: "https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.1/jquery.min.js"}
    %script{src: "js/boxlayout.js"}
    :javascript
      $(function() {
        Boxlayout.init();
      });
